- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes an algorithm for monitoring regular languages, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper provides a full implementation of the algorithm and a benchmark to evaluate its efficiency, which are topics related to software engineering.
